\nAdditionally, it is shown that the residence time of $q$-$r$ CMTs through\ndifferent topologies correlate well with the corresponding population\nfractions. These findings not only lead to improved understanding of non-local\ndynamics, but also provide an important foundation for developing Lagrangian\nvelocity-gradient models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 1 Feb 2020 19:18:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-24"}
